The paper deals with the secrecy capacity of a communication channel, which is a topic in information theory (cs.IT) and cryptography (cs.CR). The use of multi-antenna technology is also a key aspect of the paper, which could place it in the sub-categories of multimedia (cs.MM), networking and internet architecture (cs.NI), and signal processing (cs.SI).
